Data-FormValidator-Filters-HTMLScrubber version 0.02
====================================================

Data-FormValidator-Filters-HTMLScrubber is a Data-FormValidator
filter that allows to scrub/sanitize html form field values.

CHANGES FROM PREVIOUS VERSION

	+ Added docs and test
	
See 'Changes' file in this distribution for complete history revision.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

- Data::FormValidator
- HTML::Scrubber

